interest_explanation: The updates to Tabnine's documentation primarily focus on minor technical adjustments, including the introduction of authentication token sign-in and enhanced reporting capabilities with CSV-based reports (V2). These changes indicate incremental improvements rather than breakthrough innovations or significant business impacts.
